{{Quote|They signed on under General Antilles. If they had paid attention to him, most if not all of them would still be alive. If you want to know who betrayed your people to death, look to the commander who broke ranks.|[[Jagged Fel]], to [[Lensi]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: The Final Prophecy">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Final Prophecy]]''</ref>}}
The '''''Redheart''''' was a [[Duros/Legends|Duros]]-crewed warship operated by the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances]] during the later stages of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. ''Redheart'' was part of a task force commanded by [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] during an [[Battle of the Duro system|operation]] over [[Duro/Legends|Duro]] in [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]]. It was one of several ships lost when a portion of Antilles' fleet and some local Duros resistance fighters refused an order to fall back.

